HEADWORD: Picard
<hw>Pic"ard</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Eccl. Hist.)</fld>
<def>One of a sect of Adamites in the fifteenth century; -- so called
from one <xex>Picard</xex> of Flanders. See <er>Adamite</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

